372
00:53:05,437 --> 00:53:06,392
Gros porc.

373
00:53:13,317 --> 00:53:14,545
Anne ?

374
00:53:14,757 --> 00:53:17,555
Tu veux un Coca au distributeur ?

375
00:54:23,637 --> 00:54:26,674
